@page "/azure-services"

<style>
    body {
        background-color: #000;
        color: #f8ebc9;
    }

    .services-container {
        padding: 40px;
        text-align: center;
        background-color: #0d0d0d;
        border-radius: 20px;
        box-shadow: 0 0 20px rgba(247, 239, 195, 0.4);
        margin: 40px auto;
        max-width: 1000px;
        transition: all 0.3s ease-in-out;
        margin-top: 7rem;
    }

    .services-container:hover {
        box-shadow: 0 0 40px rgba(247, 239, 195, 0.4);
    }

    h1 {
        color: #f1e4b7;
        font-size: 3.5rem;
        margin-bottom: 10px;
        text-shadow: 0 0 15px rgba(247, 239, 195, 0.822);
    }

    p {
        color: #dcdcdc;
        font-size: 1.2rem;
    }

    .section {
        margin-top: 30px;
        background-color: #1a1a1a;
        border-radius: 15px;
        padding: 20px;
        transition: transform 0.3s ease;
    }

    .section:hover {
        transform: scale(1.02);
        background-color: #222;
    }

    .section-title {
        color: #f1e4b7;
        font-size: 2.5rem;
        margin-bottom: 10px;
        border-bottom: 2px solid #f1e4b7;
        font-family: "Arizonia";
    }

    ul {
        list-style: none;
        padding: 0;
    }

    li {
        background-color: #111;
        border-left: 4px solid #f1e4b7;
        margin: 10px 0;
        padding: 10px;
        color: #f0f0f0;
        border-radius: 6px;
        transition: background-color 0.3s ease, transform 0.2s ease;
    }

    li:hover {
        background-color: #333;
        transform: translateX(5px);
    }

</style>

<div class="services-container">
    <h1>Azure Services Overview</h1>
    <p>
        Our project leverages several Azure services to deliver scalability, AI-driven insights, 
        secure storage, and seamless deployment. Each service plays a key role in the overall architecture.
    </p>

    <div class="section">
        <div class="section-title">AI and Cognitive Services</div>
        <ul>
            <li>
                <b>Azure AI Vision</b> — Used for intelligent food image labelling and categorization within our FastAPI AI module.
            </li>
            <li>
                <b>Azure AI Search</b> — Enables context-aware and semantic search across donations, NGOs, and food categories.
            </li>
        </ul>
    </div>

    <div class="section">
        <div class="section-title">Application Hosting & Deployment</div>
        <ul>
            <li>
                <b>Azure Container Apps</b> — Used to deploy both the NestJS backend and the FastAPI AI service for scalable containerized workloads.
            </li>
            <li>
                <b>Azure Static Web Apps</b> — Hosts the ReactJS-based frontend, providing global availability and automatic CI/CD integration.
            </li>
            <li>
                <b>Azure App Service</b> — Used for web hosting and to run our Blazor demo for this assignment.
            </li>
        </ul>
    </div>

    <div class="section">
        <div class="section-title">Storage and Data Management</div>
        <ul>
            <li>
                <b>Azure Blob Storage</b> — Stores uploaded food images and large binary data for AI processing.
            </li>
            <li>
                <b>Azure Cosmos DB</b> — Provides globally distributed, low-latency data storage for user, NGO, and donation data.
            </li>
        </ul>
    </div>

    <div class="section">
        <div class="section-title">Integration and Security</div>
        <ul>
            <li>
                <b>Azure Functions</b> — Handles background event-driven operations such as notifications and data synchronization.
            </li>
            <li>
                <b>Azure Maps</b> — Supports proximity-based routing to connect donors and recipients efficiently.
            </li>
            <li>
                <b>Azure Key Vault</b> — Safeguards API keys, database credentials, and other application secrets.
            </li>
        </ul>
    </div>

    <p style="margin-top:30px;color:#ccc;">
        Each of these Azure components ensures that our system remains intelligent, secure, and cloud-native.
    </p>
</div>
